<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270240>
    dc:description "Figs 1 - 6. Lonchoptera vaillanti sp. nov., male. 2. male genitalia, dorsal view - 3. same, ventral view - 4. same, detail, scale is same as for fig 1. — 5. left anterior gonapophysis - 6. apex of left posterior gonapophysis - 1. ventral view of segments 2 - 5 of right fore tarsus. Figs 5 and 6 are not to scale. aG, anterior gonapophysis; C, cercus; P proctiger; pG, posterior gonapophysis; S 9, sternite IX; T 9, tergite IX." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/270240/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

